e%20time.%20Buettner%20says%20that%20is%20the%20key%20to%20lasting%20change%2C%20enjoying%20what%20you%20eat%2C%20and%20feeling%20satisfied%20with%20healthy%20choices%20instead%20of%20deprived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20worry%20if%20your%20passport%20isn't%20quite%20as%20worn%20as%20his%2C%20either.%20He%20suggests%20that%20anyone%20looking%20to%20improve%20their%20cooking%20skills%20this%20year%20should%20go%20out%20and%20find%20a%20whole%20food%2C%20plant-based%20cookbook%20that%20appeals%20to%20you.%20Then%20flag%2012%20recipes%20to%20try%20before%20the%20month%20is%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCook%20three%20recipes%20every%20Sunday%20for%20a%20month%2C%20recipes%20that%20look%20delicious%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%2C%20you'll%20have%20achieved%20three%20things%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skills%20to%20cook%2012%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20know%20you%20have%20the%20hardware%20to%20cook%20those%2C%20because%20you'll%20have%20cooked%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20have%20the%20experience%20of%20tasting%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBuettner%20says%20that%20last%20piece%2C%20the%20lived%20experience%20and%20enjoyment%2C%20is%20especially%20key%20to%20your%20success.%20Nutrition%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhealthy-and-cheap-snack-ideas-to-make-at-home-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ediet%20experts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20generally%20agree%2C%20saying%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-meal-prep-recipes-fat-loss-muscle-gain-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emeal%20prep%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20planning%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20creating%20a%20sustainable%2C%20healthy%20eating%20routine.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Sunday%20part%20of%20his%20tip%20is%20just%20about%20creating%20a%20specific%2C%20actionab