0other%20Americans%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamainternalmedicine%2Ffullarticle%2F648593%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%2010%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example.%20They%20keep%20up%20healthy%20routines%20for%20life%20because%20they%20%3Cem%3Eenjoy%3C%2Fem%3E%20them%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-blue-zone-grocery-store-healthy-eating-easy-and-cheap-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20see%20healthy%20eating%20as%20an%20extra%20chore%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20longevity%2C%20there's%20no%20short-term%20fix%2C%26quot%3B%20Buettner%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20think%20about%20things%20that%20will%20be%20in%20your%20life%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20a%20good%20recipe%20and%20a%20good%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-year-diet-advice-habit-blue-zone-researcher-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704278581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6594761aab6f2ebb11f842c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-year-diet-advice-habit-blue-zone-researcher-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20guy%20who's%20traveled%20to%20the%20world's%20Blue%20Zones%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years%20says%20ditch%20the%20New%20Year's%20diet%2C%20and%20learn%20to%20cook%20healthy%20food%20you'll%20actually%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-year-diet-advice-habit-blue-zone-researcher-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22E-commerce%20firm%20Meesho%20recruits%20150%20during%20campus%20hiring%2C%20to%20take%20in%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2