0was%20not%20a%20surprise%20that%20the%20Stanley%20was%20a%20popular%20gift%3B%20I%20did%20a%20similar%20haul%20report%20last%20year%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-cup-survived-car-fire-offered-new-car-bottle-brand-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanley%20was%20very%20popular%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%2C%20too.%20What%20was%20surprising%20was%20the%20fervor%20a%20water%20bottle%20caused%2C%20especially%20among%20tweens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2011%2C%20I%20asked%20for%20dolls.%20Today's%2011-year-olds%20asked%20for%20Stanley%20tumblers.%20I%20remember%20crying%20when%20I%20got%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-girl-dolls-history-evolution-brand-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Girl%20doll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20understand%20that%20gifts%20can%20elicit%20emotional%20reactions%20in%20young%20people%2C%20but%20seeing%20Gen%20Alpha%20kids%20sobbing%20over%20water%20bottles%20is%20pretty%20surprising.%20At%20least%20the%20kids%20are%20hydrating!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20age%20range%20you%20were%20noticing%20most%20getting%20these%20Stanley%20cups%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMostly%20college-age%20and%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20first%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20Stanley%20cup%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20elder%20millennial%20suburban%20mom%20thing.%20(To%20be%20fair%2C%20this%20may%20reflect%20my%20own%20bias.)%20Is%20it%20possible%20this%20is%20a%20trend%20that%20trickled%20down%20from%20millennials%20to%20Gen%20Z%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOh%2C%20that's%20interesting.%20Hmm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20definitely%20possible%20that%20it%20trickled%20down%20from%20millennial%20moms%2C%20though%20that%20kind%20of%20defies%20how%20trends%20usually%20play%20out%20%E2%80%94%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20most%20trends%20start%20with%20cool%20youth%2C%20and%20then%20once%20they%20trickle%20down%20(to%20younger%20kids)%20and%20up%20(to%20adults)%2C%20the%20cool%20youth%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20in%20the%20lifetime%20of%20a%20trend%20cycle%20for%20a%20status%20item%20like%20a%20Stanley%20cup%3A%20Where%20are%20we%20in%20the%20cycle%3F%20Are%20they%20on%20their%20way%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20absolutely%20on%20their%20way%20out.%20This%20is%20peak%20Stanley.%20There's%20no%20up%20from%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20how%2C%20like%2C%20middle%20schoolers%20suddenly%20having%20them%20makes%20it%20seem%20uncool%20for%20the%20older%20teens%20and%2020-somethings%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExactly%20that!%20It's%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdrunk-elephant-protini-new-lotion-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrunk%20Elephant%20skincare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20young%20kids%20and%20tweens%20adopt%20a%20trend%20or%20product%2C%20teens%20and%20older%20Gen%20Z%20distance%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUh%20oh%2C%20does%20this%20mean%20Drunk%20Elephant%20isn't%20cool%20anymore%3F!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrunk-elephant-founder-tiffany-masterson-shares-tips-for-success-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrunk%20Elephant%20isn't%20cool%3C%2Fa%3E%20anymore.%20%3A%2F%20In%202021%2C%20I%20interviewed%20Gen%20Zers%20about%20what%20skincare%20they%20were%20buying%2C%20and%20a%2015-year-old%20told%20me%20Drunk%20Elephant%20is%20overhyped%20and%20for%20%26quot%3B12-year-olds%20that%20want%20to%20be%2015-year-olds.%26quot%3B%20Ouch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20might%20be%20the%20next%20cool%20water%20bottle%3F%20Or%20will%20there%20even%20be%20another%20trendy%20water%20bottle%3F%20Maybe%20everyone%20will%20just%20drink%20from%2C%20like%20%E2%80%A6%20a%20glass%3F%20Or%20will%20people%20move%20onto%2C%20like%2C%20status%20p