%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPilat%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20New%20York%20and%20San%20Francisco%2C%20says%20she%20works%20out%20of%20SpaceX's%20headquarters%20in%20Hawthorne%20and%20travels%20there%20every%20few%20weeks.%20She%20stays%20for%20about%20a%20week%20and%20creates%20paintings%20in%20a%20space%20she%20shares%20with%20the%20industrial%20design%20team.%20Her%20paintings%20hang%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20doesn't%20have%20an%20official%20artist-in-residence%20program.%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20a%20bit%20of%20convincing%2C%20finding%20the%20right%20connections%2C%20and%20presenting%20a%20vision%20that%20aligned%20with%20a%20mission%20of%20space%20exploration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20her%20view%2C%20her%20presence%20at%20SpaceX%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20only%20a%20privilege%26quot%3B%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bresponsibility%20to%20give%20technology%20a%20voice.%26quot%3B%20She%20thinks%20that's%20because%20society%20is%20concerned%20with%20how%20tech%20is%20rapidly%20advancing%20and%20the%20power%20it%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENo%20other%20artist%20has%20ever%20been%20given%20such%20unprecedented%20access%2C%20Pilat%20said%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pilat's%20artwork%20from%20her%20residency%20at%20SpaceX%20-%20a%20blue%20painting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65786e7358e7c0c29a2c01f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPilat's%20artwork%20from%20her%20residency%20at%20SpaceX.%3Cp%3EPilat%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20SpaceX%2C%20Pilat%20created%20large-scale%20portrait%20paintings%20of%20the%20Dragon%20Hatch%2C%20the%20door%20on%20top%20of%20its%20Dragon%20Capsule%20in%20a%20series%20titled%20%26quot%3BInfinite.%26quot%3B%20She%20toured%20the%20entire%20SpaceX%20factory%20with%20the%20team%20and%20looked%20at%20various%20machinery%20and%20parts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20first%20visit%20was%20extraordinary%2C%20witnessing%20so%20many%20brilliant%20minds%20collaboratively%20crafting%20technology%20that%20once%20would%20have%20seemed%20miraculous%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20divine%20experience%2C%20inspiring%20me%20to%20create%20divine%20paintings.%20Religion%20and%20technology%20share%20numerous%20similarities%3A%20their%20power%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20brighter%20future%2C%20and%20their%20esoteric%20nature%20to%20those%20unfamiliar%20with%20them.%20I%20view%20engineers%20as%20the%20high%20priests%20of%20technology.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Infinite%20series%20embodies%20divine%20iconography%20and%20she%20used%20gold%20leaf%20and%20halos.%20The%20paintings%20are%20diptychs%20%E2%80%94%20made%20up%20of%20two%20halves%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20says%20symbolizes%20%26quot%3Bthe%20duality%20of%20sin%20and%20redemption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERobotics%20hold%20a%20special%20place%20in%20her%20heart%20because%20of%20its%20cultural%20impact%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20paintings%20created%20by%20the%20robot%20dogs%20pictured%20behind%20Agnieszka%20Pilat%20and%20two%20robot%20dogs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657874937a3c8094d5dc03db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPilat%20is%20a%20Polish-American%20artist%20with%20an%20interest%20in%20tech%3Cp%3EKim%20Landy%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20NGV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20artist%20said%20that%20with%20robotics'%20integration%20of%20AI%2C%20they%20represent%20a%20crucial%20juncture%20in%20AI's%20evolution%20from%20the%20digital%20realm%20to%20the%20physical%20world.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BMost%20AI%20exists%20in%20the%20cloud%2C%20but%20robots%20make%20it%20tangible%20and%20present%20in%20our%20daily%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20transition%20from%20digital%20to%20physical%20is%20what%20sparks%20the%20most%20fascinating%20discussions.%20Being%20an%20artist%2C%20being%20part%20of%20these%20conversations%2C%20perhaps%20even%20leading%20them%2C%20is%20incredibly%20exciting%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPilat%20has%20her%20own%20robot%20dog%20named%20Basia%20that%20she%20takes%20for%20walks%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Artist%20Agnieszka%20Pilat%20petting%20one%20of%20two%20robotic%20dogs%20pictured%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65646e31fe5bc6545ebc2ba8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223507%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAgnieszka%20Pilat%20trained%20the%20robot%20dogs%20to%20paint.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20West%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20people%20who%20meet%20her%20and%20Basia%20in%20person%20are%20curious%2C%20and%20stop%20to%20ask%20questions%20and%20take%20photos%20or%20videos.%C2%A0However%2C%20some%20people%20online%20write%20mean%20comments%20under%20videos%20of%20them%20posted%20of%20them%20online.%20Sometimes%20they%20accuse%20Pilat%20of%20surveillance%20and%20warn%20about%20robots%20taking%20over.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BThey%20even%20threaten%20to%20smash%20Basia%20or%20throw%20her%20into%20a%20river%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaintings-created-by-robot-dogs-trained-by-former-spacex-artist-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704276001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657947210ec98e92f74eda11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaintings-created-by-robot-dogs-trained-by-former-spacex-artist-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agnieszka%20Pilat%20trained%20