%20platforms%20in%20the%20world.%20Khanmigo%20can%20help%20guide%20students%20to%20correct%20answers%20over%20chats%20and%20provide%20technology-enhanced%20essay%20feedback%2C%20grading%2C%20lesson%20planning%2C%20and%20rubric%20creation%20for%20teachers.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20put%20the%20right%20guardrails%2C%20we%20can%20mitigate%20the%20risks.%20But%20I%20think%20we're%20at%20the%20cusp%20of%20using%20AI%20for%20probably%20the%20biggest%20positive%20transformation%20that%20education%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20said%20in%20his%20April%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Fsal_khan_how_ai_could_save_not_destroy_education%2Ftranscript%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETED%20Talk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHadi%20Partovi%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hadi%20Partovi%20Code.org%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6517599a5640b20019d78918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHadi%20Partovi%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Code.org.%3Cp%3ECode.org%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20CEO%20of%20the%20nonprofit%20Code.org%2C%20Partovi%20helped%20establish%20one%20of%20the%20premiere%20organizations%20for%20teaching%20young%20people%20computer%20science%2C%20including%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning.%20In%20May%2C%20Partovi%20teamed%20up%20with%20other%20leading%20education%20companies%20and%20organizations%2C%20such%20as%20Khan%20Academy%2C%20to%20launch%20TeachAI%2C%20a%20nationwide%20effort%20to%20help%20teachers%20better%20understand%20AI%20and%20support%20its%20use%20as%20a%20classroom-learning%20tool.%20Leading%20technology%20companies%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20the%20Google-backed%20Code.org%2C%20and%20it%20has%20raised%20%24200%20million%20in%20funding.%20Partovi's%20interest%20in%20nurturing%20tech%20talent%20runs%20in%20the%20family%3A%20His%20twin%20brother%2C%20Ali%2C%20runs%20the%20startup%20accelerator%20Neo%2C%20and%20both%20brothers%20are%20prolific%20angel%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMax%20Tegmark%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Max%20Tegmark%20Future%20of%20Life%20Institute%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65175b845640b20019d78936%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMax%20Tegmark%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20MIT%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20precision%20cosmology.%3Cp%3EFuture%20of%20Life%20Institute%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETegmark%2C%20a%20Swedish-American%20physicist%20who%20has%20studied%20everything%20from%20cosmology%20to%20machine%20learning%2C%20is%20primarily%20known%20for%20his%20scientific%20research%20and%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Future%20of%20Life%20Institute%2C%20or%20FLI%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20works%20to%20reduce%20risks%20that%20come%20with%20powerful%20transformative%20technologies.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20FLI%20under%20Tegmark's%20leadership%20published%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20pause%20all%20AI-research%20experiments%20more%20powerful%20than%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20for%20six%20months%20to%20ensure%20that%20safety%20standards%20are%20implemented%20to%20protect%20humans%20against%20threats%20AI%20could%20pose.%20More%20than%2030%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Stability%20AI's%20Emad%20Mostaque%2C%20and%20Steve%20Wozniak%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Apple%2C%20signed%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERachel%20Thomas%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Thomas%20Fast.ai%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65175af05640b20019d78930%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Thomas%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Fast.ai.%3Cp%3EFast.ai%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20AI%20knowledge%20ac