ty%2C%20and%20inclusion%20(DEI)%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20said%20in%20his%20essay%20that%20he%20believes%20DEI%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20root%20cause%20of%20antisemitism%20at%20Harvard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20DEI%2C%20one's%20degree%20of%20oppression%20is%20determined%20based%20upon%20where%20one%20resides%20on%20a%20so-called%20intersectional%20pyramid%20of%20oppression%20where%20whites%2C%20Jews%2C%20and%20Asians%20are%20deemed%20oppressors%2C%20and%20a%20subset%20of%20people%20of%20color%2C%20LGBTQ%20people%2C%20and%2For%20women%20are%20deemed%20to%20be%20oppressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ackman%20said%20such%20a%20dichotomy%20is%2C%20in%20his%20opinion%2C%20flawed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDEI%20is%20racist%20because%20reverse%20racism%20is%20racism%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20against%20white%20people%20(and%20it%20is%20remarkable%20that%20I%20even%20need%20to%20point%20this%20out)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ideology%2C%20he%20surmised%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20societal%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20country%20has%20seen%20burgeoning%20resentment%20and%20anger%20grow%20materially%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20and%20the%20DEI%20movement%20is%20an%20important%20contributor%20to%20our%20growing%20divisiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResentment%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20drivers%20of%20racism.%20And%20it%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20equity%2C%20i.e%2C%20fairness%2C%20in%20how%20DEI%20operates%2C%20that%20contributes%20to%20this%20resentment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20then%20called%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20Harvard%20Corporation%20Board%20members%20who'd%20backed%20Gay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20should%20not%20be%20principally%20comprised%20of%20individuals%20who%20share%20the%20same%20politics%20and%20views%20about%20DEI%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20board%20members%20should%20be%20chosen%20in%20a%20transparent%20process%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20the%2030-person%20Board%20of%20Overseers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20the%20university's%20Office%20of%20Diversity%2C%20Equity%2C%20Inclusion%2C%20and%20Belonging%20should%20also%20be%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20light%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20news%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20try%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20and%20provide%20perspective%20on%20what%20this%20is%20really%20all%20about.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20first%20became%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHarvard%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Harvard%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%2034%20Harvard%20student%20organizations%2C%20early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20October%208th%20before%20Israel%20had%20taken%20any%20military%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bill%20Ackman%20(%40BillAckman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1742441534627184760%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Ackman%20has%20communicated%20his%20thoughts%20via%20a%20lengthy%20online%20message.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1720987581549080965%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1731532031048245631%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1733985787455168906%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5