tch%2C%20otherwise%2C%20I%20will%20have%20you%20removed%20from%20the%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20declared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20question%20the%20advocate's%20usual%20practices%2C%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20do%20you%20normally%20appear%3F%20Is%20this%20the%20way%20you%20shout%20at%20judges%20every%20time%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20decorum%20in%20the%20courtroom%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20lower%20your%20pitch%20first.%20If%20you%20think%20you%20can%20browbeat%20us%20by%20raising%20your%20voice%2C%20you're%20mistaken.%20It%20has%20not%20happened%20in%2023%20years%3B%20it%20will%20not%20happen%20in%20the%20last%20year%20of%20my%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advocate%2C%20taken%20aback%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20stern%20warning%2C%20promptly%20apologised%20and%20proceeded%20with%20his%20submissions%20in%20a%20more%20courteous%20manner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20incident%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20asked%20to%20maintain%20the%20decorum%20of%20the%20courtroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20another%20occasion%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20a%20lawyer%20talking%20on%20the%20mobile%20phone%20inside%20his%20courtroom.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20market%20that%20you%20are%20talking%20on%20the%20phone.%20Confiscate%20his%20mobile%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20last%20year%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20reportedly%20%26quot%3Bshouted%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20voice%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20senior%20advocate%20Vikas%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20urging%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20push%20up%20a%20case%20related%20to%20land%20for%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20furious%2C%20snapped%3A%20%26quot%3BKeep%20quiet.%20Leave%20this%20court%20right%20now.%20You%20cannot%20cower