20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20questioning%2C%20the%20accused%20revealed%20that%20they%20initially%20stayed%20in%20Varanasi%20for%20a%20week%20after%20the%20incident%20but%20left%20town%20as%20student%20protests%20intensified.%20They%20returned%20about%2015%20days%20ago%2C%20believing%20the%20situation%20had%20cooled%20down.%20The%20accused%20evaded%20capture%20by%20hiding%20in%20various%20locations%20around%20the%20city%20before%20finally%20returning%20to%20their%20respective%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20documents%20indicate%20that%20a%20motorcycle%20allegedly%20used%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20three%20phones%2C%20some%20cash%2C%20and%20jewellery%20were%20confiscated%20during%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused.%20Varanasi%20Commissioner%20Mutha%20Ashok%20Jain%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20case%20or%20the%20investigation%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fiit-bhu-sexual-assault-case-accused-involved-in-3-other-molestations-on-campus-9092574%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20the%20chapter%20is%20closed.%20We%20have%20arrested%20the%20accused.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704267707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03130344%2FCopy-of-Copy-of-Lead-image-size-5.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fiit-bhu-accused-confess-to-3-other-molestations-visited-campus-looking-for-opportunities-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kunal%20Pandey%2C%20Saksham%20Patel%2C%20and%20Abhishek%20Chauhan%20revealed%20during%20police%20questioning%20that%20they%20regularly%20visited%20the%20university%20premises%20between%2011%20pm%20and%201%20am%2C%20'Indian%20Express'%20has%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fiit-bhu-accused-confess-to-3-other-molestations-visited-campus-looking-for-opportunities-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20'Wake%20Up%20Sid'%20sequel%20on%20the%20cards%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704267638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106508422%2Cimgsize-41280.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fis-ranbir-kapoor-and-konkana-sen-sharmas-wake-up-sid-sequel-on-the-cards-karan-johar-drops-hits-watch%2Farticleshow%2F106508412.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106508412.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKaran%20Johar%20surprises%20fans%20with%20a%20teaser%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20and%20Konkona%20Sen%20Sharma's%20possible%20film%20project.%20The%20video%20hints%20at%20something%20exciting%20brewing%20between%20the%20two%20actors%20after%2015%20years.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20confirmed%20to%20be%20a%20sequel%20to%20'Wake%20Up%20Sid'%2C%20fans%20are%20eagerly%20awaiting%20official%20announcements.%20Recent%20viral%20videos%20of%20Ranbir%20and%20Konkona%20on%20the%20film%20sets%20have%20sparked%20anticipation%20and%20speculation%20among%20their%20fan%20base.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fis-ranbir-kapoor-and-konkana-sen-sharmas-wake-up-sid-sequel-on-the-cards-karan-johar-drops-hits-watch%2Farticleshow%2F106508412.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Lessons%20From%20Judgment%20On%20Hindenburg%20-%20For%20Adani%20And%20His%20Detractors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20in%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20lesson%20to%20India's%20politically-driven%20litigators%20who%20often%20drag%20the%20judiciary%20into%20a%20fishing%20expedition%20in%20matters%20that%20are%20better%20left%20to%20other%20agencies%20to%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefly%2C%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20which%20specialises%20in%20greenmailing%20and%20short-selling%20to%20make%20big%20bucks%20by%20targeting%20vulnerable%20companies%2C%20released%20a%20damaging%20report%20last%20January%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20report%20alleged%20that%20the%20world's%20(then)%20third%20wealthiest%20conglomerate%20was%20%26quot%3Bpulling%20the%20largest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%26quot%3B.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20the%20report%20(read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%20alleged%20that%20the%20group%20manipulated%20stock%20prices%2C%20used%20shell%20companies%20to%20route%20questionable%20transactions%2C%20and%20indulged%20in%20accounting%20fraud%20to%20get%20where%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20overactive%20public%20interest%20litigators%2C%20ever%20keen%20to%20see%20a%20Narendra%20Modi%20connection%20behind%20Adani's%20meteoric%20rise%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20immediately%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demanding%20that%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20be%20investigated%20by%20a%20court-monitored%20agency%2C%20and%20not%20the%20usual%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20delivered%20today%20(3%20January%202024)%20by%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20and%20Manoj%20Mishra%2C%20made%20five%20important%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20probes%20already%20initiated%20by%20SEBI%2C%20the%20market%20watchdog%2C%20which%20has%20completed%2022%20of%20the%2024%20cases.%20The%20court%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20complete%20the%20remaining%20two%20in%20three%20months%2C%20and%20take%20whatever%20action%20was%20needed.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20sent%20a%20powerful%20message%20that%20it%20will%20not%20meddle%20with%20regulators%20who%20are%20already%20functioning%20per%20law%20when%20no%20evidence%20to%20the%20contrary%20was%20provided%20by%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETwo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20consequently%20ruled%20that%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20transfer%20the%20cases%20from%20SEBI%20to%20an%20external%20agency%20like%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThree%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20summarily%20rejected%20the%20allegation%20that%20there%20was%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20supervisory%20panel%20it%20had%20set%20up%20to%20monitor%20the%20SEBI%20investigations.%20The%20panel%20had%20six%20members%2C%20two%20former%20judges%2C%20AM%20Sapre%20and%20JP%20Devdhar%2C%20two%20former%20bankers%20(KV%20Kamath%20and%20OP%20Bhat)%2C%20a%20tech%20titan%20(Nandan%20Nilekani)%20and%20an%20expert%20on%20regulation%2C%20Somasekhar%20Sundaresan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFour%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20also%20found%20no%20valid%20ground%20to%20reject%20SEBI's%20amended%20regulations%20for%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%2C%20where%20norms%20had%20actually%20been%20tightened%20and%20not%20loosened%2C%20as%20alleged%20by%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFive%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20judges%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20could%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20proof%20of%20hanky-panky.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20SEBI%20could%20act%20against%20Hindenburg%20in%20case%20it%20was%20found%20to%20have%20flouted%20any%20Indian%20law%20while%20doing%20its%20short-selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lessons%20in%20this%20for%20the%20Adani%20group%20too%2C%20the%20most%20important%20of%20which%20is%20that%20it%20must%20rely%20less%20on%20debt%20to%20fund%20its%20expansion%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20is%20focused%20on%20capital-intensive%20areas%20like%20infrastructure%20and%20utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20in%20February%2C%20New%20York%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business's%20valuation%20guru%2C%20Aswath%20Damodaran%2C%20wrote%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faswathdamodaran.substack.com%2Fp%2Fcontrol-complexity-and-politics-deconstructing%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20where%20he%20rejected%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20group's%20business%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcon%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20the%20business%20was%20certainly%20over-leveraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20Damodaran%20had%20this%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B...I%20find%20the%20Hindenburg%20shock-and-awe%20approach%20of%20throwing%20up%20dozens%2C%20perhaps%20hundreds%20of%20accusations%20of%20wrongdoings%20at%20a%20firm%2C%20hoping%20that%20something%20sticks%2C%20off-putting%2C%20since%20even%20if%20I%20am%20in%20agreement%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20spending%20time%20trying%20to%20separate%20the%20wheat%20from%20the%20chaff%2C%20the%20big%20wrongdoings%20from%20the%20minor%20distractions%E2%80%A6.%20Hindenburg%20should%20be%20complimented%20for%20their%20legwork%2C%20but%20their%20critique%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20rests%20on%20a%20mix%20of%20serious%20contentions%2C%20circumstantial%20evidence%20and%20questionable%20claims%E2%80%A6.To%20be%20able%20to%20manipulate%20and%20move%20the%20market%20capitalisation%20of%20a%20company%20by%20a%20hundred%20billion%2C%20roughly%20the%20increase%20in%20value%20in%202022%2C%20you%20would%20expect%20to%20see%20huge%20numbers%20of%20shares%20being%20traded%20by%20these%20entities%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20see%20that%E2%80%A6.the%20questionable%20claims%20are%20the%20ones%20to%20do%20with%20earnings%20manipulation%2C%20since%20if%20Adani%20is%20manipulating%20earnings%2C%20it%20is%20not%20doing%20a%20very%20good%20job%2C%20reporting%20low%20margins%20and%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20well%20to%20nip%20the%20litigators'%20mischief%20in%20the%20bud%2C%20for%20the%20last%20thing%20one%20needs%20is%20a%20well-publicised%20witch-hunt%20against%20one%20of%20India's%20biggest%20conglomerates%2C%20albeit%20one%20that%20grew%20too%20big%20and%20too%20fast%20and%20with%20less%20capital%20than%20most%20others.%20If%20anything%20wrong%20had%20been%20done%20by%20the%20group%2C%20the%20market%20regulator%20is%20competent%20enough%20to%20investigate%20and%20take%20action.%20The%20court%20did%20well%20to%20uphold%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20regulatory%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Raghavan%20Jagannathan%20is%20currently%20Editorial%20Director%20of%20Swarajya%20magazine.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704267360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fs0b4ma78_adani-reports-_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flessons-from-judgment-on-hindenburg-for-adani-and-his-detractors-4791792%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20in%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20lesson%20to%20India's%20politically-driven%20litigators%20who%20often%20drag%20the%20judiciary%20into%20a%20fishing%20expedition%20in%20matters%20that%20are%20better%20left%20to%20other%20agencies%20to%20deal%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flessons-from-judgment-on-hindenburg-for-adani-and-his-detractors-4791792%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flessons-from-judgment-on-hindenburg-for-adani-and-his-detractors-4791792%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flessons-from-judgment-on-hindenburg-for-adani-and-his-detractors-4791792%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wh