20milk%20and%20groceries%2C%20prompted%20authorities%20to%20expedite%20the%20dispatch%20of%20petrol%20tankers%20to%20replenish%20gas%20stations%20as%20many%20petrol%20pumps%20across%20the%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ffuel-pumps-running-dry-across-india-amid-widespread-protests-bytruckdrivers-101704187355024.html%5C%22%3Ewere%20running%20out%20of%20fuel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20did%20not%20remain%20limited%20to%20bus%20and%20druck%20drivers%2C%20with%20taxi%2C%20auto-rickshaw%20and%20other%20passenger%20vehicle%20drivers%20adding%20their%20voices%20to%20the%20collective%20grievance%2C%20compounding%20challenges%20for%20the%20public.%20According%20to%20Vijay%20Kalaria%2C%20former%20vice%20president%20(western%20region)%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%2C%20around%20five%20lakh%20vehicles%20came%20to%20a%20standstill%20in%20the%20state.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rajesh%20Sen%2C%20general%20Sscretary%20of%20the%20Bus%20Drivers%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20revealed%20that%20there%20was%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20bus%20owners%2C%20threatening%20job%20termination%20if%20drivers%20did%20not%20resume%20operations.%20Despite%20the%20pressure%2C%20the%20drivers%20remained%20steadfast%2C%20unwilling%20to%20yield%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruck%20drivers%20discontent%20with%20the%20stringent%20provision%20initiated%20a%20coordinated%20strike%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20including%20Maharashtra%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20vehicles%20remained%20off%20the%20roads%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20half%20a%20day.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Bilaspur%2C%20truck%20drivers%20resorted%20to%20burning%20tyres%20on%20the%20roads%20in%20protest.%20Protests%20by%20drivers%20were%20evident%20in%20various%20districts%20of%20Bihar%2C%20including%20the%20capital%20city%20Patna.%20Truck%20drivers%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20created%20traffic%20jams%20in%20solidarity.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20truck%20drivers%20staged%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Erasta%20roko%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20demonstrations%20at%20various%20locations%2C%20heightening%20concerns%20about%20potential%20fuel%20shortages.%20Officials%20reported%20a%20temporary%20blockage%20of%20traffic%20on%20the%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20Highway%20in%20the%20Mira%20Bhayandar%20area%20of%20Thane%20district%20by%20the%20protesting%20truck%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversial%20clause%20106%20and%20the%20questions%20it%20raises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20in%20question%20%E2%80%93%20clause%20106%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20%E2%80%93%20came%20under%20scrutiny%20as%20a%20majority%20of%20opposition%20MPs%20had%20vacated%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20a%20walkout.%20Seizing%20the%20opportunity%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20swiftly%20pushed%20the%20Bill%20through%20with%20a%20voice%20vote%2C%20sidestepping%20any%20deliberation%20or%20discourse.%20This%20manoeuvre%20drew%20criticism%20for%20flouting%20parliamentary%20norms%20and%20undermining%20the%20democratic%20process.%20Protests%20ensued%2C%20with%20MPs%20and%20activists%20calling%20for%20a%20thorough%20review%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%20joint%20committee.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20at%20the%20time%20stood%20its%20ground%20and%20refused%20to%20budge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClause%20106%20of%20the%20BNS%20introduces%20a%20provision%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20the%20rate%20of%20hit-and-run%20accidents%2C%20which%20annually%20claim%20approximately%2050%2C000%20lives%20in%20India.%20Clause%20106%20of%20the%20Bill%20states%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(1)%20Whoever%20causes%20death%20of%20any%20person%20by%20doing%20any%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20five%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(2)%20Whoever%20causes%20death%20of%20any%20person%20by%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving%20of%20vehicle%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20and%20escapes%20without%20reporting%20it%20to%20a%20police%20officer%20or%20a%20Magistrate%20soon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20of%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20ten%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20detractors%20argue%20that%20this%20clause%20may%20not%20serve%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20best%20interests%20due%20to%20several%20reasons%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELack%20of%20clarity%20in%20defining%20what%20constitutes%20a%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIgnoring%20the%20degree%20of%20negligence%2C%20harm%20caused%2C%20or%20the%20offender%E2%80%99s%20intention.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPotential%20for%20arbitrary%20and%20excessive%20prosecution%2C%20especially%20in%20cases%20like%20road%20accidents%20or%20medical%20negligence.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDeterrence%20of%20assistance%20in%20emergency%20situations%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20legal%20repercussions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERisk%20of%20undermining%20proportionality%20and%20fairness%20in%20criminal%20justice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20severe%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20for%20drivers%20who%20flee%20the%20accident%20scene%20or%20neglect%20to%20report%20the%20incident%20to%20authorities%20might%20dissuade%20individuals%20from%20aiding%20victims%20or%20admitting%20fault%2C%20fearing%20legal%20repercussions%20or%20public%20backlash.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEstablishing%20a%20presumption%20of%20guilt%20for%20drivers%20involved%20in%20hit-and-run%20cases%2C%20requiring%20them%20to%20prove%20their%20innocence%20in%20court.%20This%20approach%20raises%20concerns%20about%20violating%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20the%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial%2C%20as%20the%20onus%20of%20proof%20traditionally%20rests%20with%20the%20prosecution%2C%20not%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFailing%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20road%20accidents%2C%20such%20as%20inadequate%20infrastructure%2C%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20corruption%20or%20negligence.%20Rather%20than%20emphasising%20prevention%20and%20education%2C%20Clause%20106%20leans%20on%20deterrence%20and%20retribution%2C%20which%20may%20prove%20insufficient%20in%20reducing%20hit-and-run%20incidents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20reassures%20truckers%2C%20urges%20them%20to%20return%20to%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1992552%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20late%20in%20the%20evening%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20government%20declared%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20concerns%20of%20truckers%20regarding%20the%20provision%20of%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20fine%2C%20under%20Section%20106%20(2)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20and%20held%20detailed%20discussion%20with%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20today.%20The%20government%20wants%20to%20point%20out%20that%20these%20new%20laws%20and%20provisions%20have%20not%20yet%20come%20into%20force.%20We%20would%20also%20like%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20invoke%20Section%20106%20(2)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20will%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20consultation%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress.%20We%20appeal%20to%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20and%20all%20the%20drivers%20to%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20jobs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20claimed%20transparency%2C%20vowing%20to%20withhold%20enforcement%20of%20a%20disputed%20clause%20pending%20a%20decision%2C%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%20paradoxically%20lauded%20the%20same%20clause%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%202%2C%202023%2C%20the%20BJP%20party%20from%20their%20official%20X%20handle%20posted%2C%20%E2%80%9CAvoid%20being%20influenced%20by%20others.%20Understand%20hit%20and%20run%20laws!%20These%20new%20laws%20are%20designed%20to%20save%20more%20lives%20in%20road%20accidents.%20They%20will%20apply%20to%20all%20vehicles%2C%20including%20two-wheelers%2C%20three-wheelers%2C%20cars%2C%20trucks%2C%20tankers%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%82%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A1%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%9D%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%A6%E