n.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Central%20Railways%20chief%20public%20relations%20officer%20Shivraj%20Manaspure%20was%20suddenly%20transferred%20on%20December%2029%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20just%20seven%20months%20after%20being%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20%E2%80%93%20soon%20after%20he%20released%20details%20on%20how%20much%20the%203D%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20at%20railway%20stations%20had%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Frailway-official-who-gave-pm-selfie-booths-cost-info-shunted%2Farticleshow%2F106494991.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Manaspure%20has%20been%20transferred%20without%20being%20given%20a%20reason%20or%20being%20told%20where%20his%20next%20posting%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railways%20is%20one%20of%2019%20zones%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Railways.%20An%20Amravati-based%20social%20activist%2C%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20had%20filed%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20queries%20with%20five%20of%20those%20zones%20%E2%80%93%20Central%20Railways%2C%20Western%2C%20Southern%2C%20Northern%2C%20and%20North%20Western%20Railways%20%E2%80%93%20asking%20for%20details%20on%20costs%20associated%20with%20the%20selfie%20booths.%20The%20Central%20Railways%20was%20the%20only%20zone%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20query%20on%20specific%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20Central%20Railway%20Zone%20alone%2C%20around%2020%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20each%2C%20totalling%20to%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%20There%20are%20another%2032%20odd%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20(