political%20bureau%2C%20Saleh%20Al-Arouri's%20journey%20was%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20imprisonment%2C%20and%20a%20tumultuous%20relationship%20with%20Israel.%20His%20death%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Beirut%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20comes%20as%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20the%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaleh%20al-Arouri's%20ascent%20to%20the%20role%20of%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20Hamas%20political%20bureau%20in%202017%20solidified%20his%20standing%20as%20a%20key%20political%20figure%20within%20the%20organisation.%20Accused%20by%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%20of%20overseeing%20Hamas's%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20his%20presence%20on%20the%20US%20list%20of%20terrorists%20since%202015%20added%20an%20international%20dimension%20to%20his%20notoriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20strike%20that%20killed%20him%20targeted%20Hamas's%20office%20in%20Dahiyeh%2C%20a%20Hezbollah%20stronghold%20in%20southern%20Beirut%2C%20Lebanon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETies%20And%20Accusations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20financing%20and%20orchestrating%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Al-Arouri%20faced%20condemnation%20from%20both%20Israel%20and%20the%20US.%20The%20US-led%20Rewards%20for%20Justice%20Program%20offered%20%245%20million%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20identification%20or%20location%2C%20highlighting%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20allegations%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20involvement%20in%20planning%20the%202014%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20of%20three%20Israeli%20teenagers%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20further%20solidified%20his%20reputation%20as%20a%20notorious%20militant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Two%20Faces%20Of%20Al-Arouri%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20Al-Arouri's%20life%20reveals%20a%20dual%20identity%20-%20a%20meticulous%2C%20bookish%20figure%20who%20was%20not%20only%20an%20organiser%20and%20militant%20but%20also%20a%20family%20man.%20Court%20records%20and%20international%20agency%20reports%20paint%20a%20complex%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20deeply%20involved%20in%20Hamas's%20military%20activities%20while%20simultaneously%20navigating%20personal%20relationships%20and%20periods%20of%20incarceration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20occasional%20claims%20of%20reform%2C%20Al-Arouri's%20actions%20spoke%20louder%20than%20words.%20His%20exile%20to%20Turkey%20and%20subsequent%20alleged%20planning%20of%20increased%20West%20Bank%20terrorism%20suggested%20a%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20Hamas's%20objectives%2C%20particularly%20through%20the%20tactic%20of%20kidnapping%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20the%20Treasury%20designated%20Al-Arouri%20as%20a%20Specially%20Designated%20Global%20Terrorist%20in%202015.%20The%20repercussions%20of%20this%20designation%20included%20the%20blocking%20of%20assets%20and%20restrictions%20on%20transactions%20involving%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPotential%20Escalation%20In%20Tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Beirut%20that%20claimed%20Al-Arouri's%20life%20marked%20a%20significant%20escalation%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20As%20the%20most%20high-profile%20figure%20to%20be%20killed%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20his%20death%20heightened%20fears%20of%20a%20wider%20regional%20blowout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20including%20Lebanon-based%20Hezbollah%2C%20vowed%20retaliation%2C%20deepening%20concerns%20about%20the%20widening%20scope%20of%20the%20conflict.%20The%20strike%20not%20only%20stirred%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20but%20also%20drew%20condemnation%20from%20Lebanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Najib%20Mikati%2C%20who%20feared%20further%20entanglement%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondemning%20Al-Arouri's%20death%2C%20Hamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20said%20that%20a%20movement%20%26quot%3Bwhose%20leaders%20fall%20as%20martyrs%20for%20the%20dignity%20of%20our%20people%20and%20our%20nation%20will%20never%20be%20defeated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20and%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20show%20many%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20Ramallah%20to%20protest%20the%20killing%20of%20Al-Arouri.%20Palestinian%20Prime%20Minister%20Mohammad%20Shtayyeh%20also%20expressed%20condemnation%2C%20emphasising%20the%20potential%20%26quot%3Brisks%20and%20consequences%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704264600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkvok5158_saleh-alarouri_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaleh-al-arouri-israel-hamas-war-israel-gaza-war-explained-top-hamas-leaders-death-in-israeli-strike-and-its-consequences-4791632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saleh%20Al-Arouri's%20journey%20was%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20imprisonment%2C%20and%20a%20tumultuous%20relationship%20with%20Israel.%20His%20death%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Beirut%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20comes%20as%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20the%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaleh-al-arouri-israel-hamas-war-israel-gaza-war-explained-top-hamas-leaders-death-in-israeli-strike-and-its-consequences-4791632%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaleh-al-arouri-israel-hamas-war-israel-gaza-war-explained-top-hamas-leaders-death-in-israeli-strike-and-its-consequences-4791632%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaleh-al-arouri-israel-hamas-war-israel-gaza-war-explained-top-hamas-leaders-death-in-israeli-strike-and-its-consequences-4791632%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Court%20Backs%20SEBI%20Clean%20Chit%20To%20Adani%20Group%20In%20Hindenburg%20Case%2C%20No%20SIT%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20huge%20victory%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20report%20by%20the%20OCCRP%20-%20an%20organisation%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20among%20others%20-%20can't%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20doubting%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI's%20investigation%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20judgment%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20there%20were%20no%20grounds%20to%20transfer%20the%20probe%20to%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20investigated%2022%20out%20of%20the%2024%20cases%20linked%20to%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research's%20allegations.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20the%20SEBI%20three%20months%20to%20complete%20investigation%20in%20the%20remaining%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20ordered%20the%20government%20and%20SEBI%20to%20check%20whether%20Hindenburg%20has%20ignored%20rules%20in%20shorting%20the%20market%20and%20to%20take%20action%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reliance%20on%20the%20OCCRP%20report%20is%20rejected%20and%20the%20reliance%20on%20a%20third-party%20organisation%20report%20without%20any%20verification%20cannot%20be%20used%20as%20proof.%20There%20are%20no%20grounds%20to%20transfer%20the%20probe%20in%20this%20case%20from%20SEBI%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20in%20the%20judgment%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20reflected%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20told%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20on%20November%2024%2C%20that%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%20and%20the%20OCCRP%20report%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%20cannot%20be%20treated%20as%20gospel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReliance%20on%20newspaper%20reports%20and%20third-party%20organisations%20to%20question%20the%20statutory%20regulator%20(SEBI)%20does%20not%20inspire%20confidence.%20They%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20inputs.%20but%20not%20conclusive%20evidence%20to%20doubt%20SEBI's%20probe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20concluding%2C%20public%20interest%20jurisprudence%20was%20developed%20to%20provide%20access%20to%20ordinary%20citizens...%20petitions%20that%20lack%20adequate%20research%20and%20rely%20on%20unsubstantiated%20reports%20cannot%20be%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqoii90kg_adani-generic_625x300_06_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20on%20the%20issue%20were%20filed%20by%20lawyers%20Vishal%20Tiwari%20and%20ML%20Sharma%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%20and%20activist%20Anamika%20Jaiswal.%20The%20petitions%20had%20claimed%20the%20Adani%20Group%20inflated%20its%20share%20prices%2C%20and%20that%20the%20shares%20of%20some%20group%20entities%20had%20fallen%20sharply%20after%20the%20report%20by%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20on%20January%2024%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20had%20termed%20the%20report%20a%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20combination%20of%20selective%20misinformation%20and%20concealed%20facts%20relating%20to%20baseless%20and%20discredited%20allegations%20to%20drive%20an%20ulterior%20motive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20explaining%20why%20it%20denied%20the%20request%20to%20transfer%20the%20probe%20to%20an%20SIT%2C%20said%20the%20investigation%20should%20be%20transferred%20only%20under%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20and%20such%20a%20power%20can't%20be%20used%20without%20a%20strong%2C%20logical%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20learning%20from%20the%20Hindenburg%20row%20is%20to%20plug%20gaps%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20Indian%20investors%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20and%20ordered%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20SEBI%20to%20use%20the%20committee's%20suggestions%20to%20strengthen%20the%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20SEBI%2C%20had%20said%20it%20had%20completed%20looking%20into%2022%20of%20the%2024%20cases%20of%20suspected%20transactions%2C%20and%20information%20from%20agencies%20abroad%20was%20awaited%20for%20the%20remaining%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20looked%20into%20India's%20regulatory%20mechanism%20to%20protect%20investors%2C%20in%20its%20report%20submitted%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20had%20also%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20said%20there%20was%20no%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20SEBI%2C%20and%20no%20price%20manipulation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20conglomerate%20had%20taken%20necessary%20steps%20to%20comfort%20retail%20investors%20amid%20severe%20market%20turmoil%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%20to%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20Adani%20group%20had%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bselective%20and%20manipulative%20presentation%20of%20matters%20already%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20create%20a%20false%20narrative%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20merely%20an%20unwarranted%20attack%20on%20any%20specific%20company%20but%20a%20calculated%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20the%20independence%2C%20integrity%20and%20quality%20of%20Indian%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20growth%20story%20and%20ambition%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704264240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2F2rnf431_adani-logo-reuters-generic-650_625x300_20_July_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hindenburg-case-supreme-court-backs-sebi-probe-4791214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20huge%20victory%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20report%20by%20the%20OCCRP%20-%20an%20organisation%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20among%20others%20-%20can't%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20doubting%20SEBI's%20investigation%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hindenburg-case-supreme-court-backs-sebi-probe-4791214%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hindenburg-case-supreme-court-backs-sebi-probe-4791214%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hindenburg-case-supreme-court-backs-sebi-probe-4791214%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Glenmark%20cuts%20diabetes%20drug%20cost%20by%2070%25%20with%20first%20Indian%20biosimilar%20launch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704264185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-08%2F14%2Ffull%2F1565801938-3166.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standa