ounter-insurgency%20operations%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Poonch%20militant%20attack%20being%20the%20latest%2C%20the%20region%20south%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20has%20seen%20an%20increased%20number%20of%20terror%20attacks%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20though%20the%20number%20is%20fewer%20than%20those%20in%20the%20Valley.%20The%20two-year%20period%20dates%20back%20to%20October%202021%20when%20nine%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20forests%20between%20Bhata%20Durian%20and%20Dehra%20Ki%20Gali%20in%20two%20separate%20firefights.%20In%20each%20of%20the%20attacks%20over%20the%20said%20period%2C%20at%20least%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20mostly%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20managed%20to%20escape%20in%20almost%20every%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Poonch%20attack%2C%20in%20which%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20in%20its%20aftermath%2C%20the%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20due%20to%20alleged%20custodial%20torture%20has%20led%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshakeup%E2%80%9D%20of%20sorts%20in%20the%20local%20command%20structure.%20Consequently%2C%20three%20security%20officers%20have%20been%20given%20marching%20orders%2C%20and%20a%20probe%20has%20been%20commissioned%20to%20get%20to%20the%20depth%20of%20what%20went%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20now%20say%20the%20Poonch%20terror%20attack%20%E2%80%93%20which%20came%20seven%20months%20after%20a%20similar%20ambush%20of%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20same%20region%20%E2%80%93%20proves%20the%20point%20that%20terrorists%20have%20been%20hiding%20in%20the%20region%20over%20a%20sustained%20period%20whilst%20successfully%20evading%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20indicates%20that%20they%20are%20extremely%20well%20trained%20and%20motivated%20and%20have%20been%20either%20able%20to%20get%20internal%20support%20for%20sustenance%20or%20gather%20intelligence%20on%20military%20movements%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20terrorists%20have%20been%20able%20to%20remain%20undetected%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20indicates%20a%20lack%20of%20actionable%20intelligence%20about%20their%20presence%2C%20infiltration%2C%20and%20replenishment%20when%20they%20are%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20they%20should%20have%20been%20on%20the%20run%20and%20should%20have%20exhausted%20all%20resources%20and%20support%20to%20have%20had%20the%20ability%20to%20strike%20again%20after%20an%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20attacks%20has%20now%20prompted%20officials%20to%20tweak%20the%20existing%20counter-insurgency%20strategy.%20%E2%80%9CCounter-terrorism%20necessitates%20constant%20evolving%20of%20tactics%20and%20operational%20methodology%20so%20as%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20the%20terrorists%20who%20always%20have%20the%20advantage%20of%20surprise%20on%20their%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704262864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Flack-of-adequate-actionable-intelligence-behind-rise-in-attacks-on-security-forces-in-jk-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Poonch%20militant%20attack%20being%20the%20latest%2C%20the%20region%20south%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20has%20seen%20an%20increased%20number%20of%20terror%20attacks%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20Top%20security%20officials%20also%20blame%20it%20on%20thinning%20of%20troops%20and%20increasing%20influx%20of%20narcotics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Flack-of-adequate-actionable-intelligence-behind-rise-in-attacks-on-security-forces-in-jk-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oil%20an%20option%20to%20recoup%20%24600%20million%20from%20