Fharvard-mit-upenn-college-presidents-response-jewish-genocide-antisemitism-israel-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGay's%20testimony%20before%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20didn't%20think%20she%20necessarily%20had%20to%20resign.%20The%20student%20pointed%20to%20what%20she%20saw%20as%20poor%20coaching%20of%20Gay%20ahead%20of%20her%20testimony.%20But%20the%20accusations%20of%20plagiarism%20proved%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20kept%20getting%20worse%20and%20worse%20and%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20student%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20claims%20about%20plagiarism.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20like%20it%20was%20sort%20of%20devaluing%20our%20degree.%20You%20go%20to%20Harvard%20for%20a%20reason%3A%20because%20it%20has%20a%20brand%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20brand%20name%2C%20she%20said%2C%20that%20Gay%20has%20tarnished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20she%20should%20have%20been%20there%20to%20begin%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20student%20added%2C%20indicating%20that%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20what%20critics%20have%20derided%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-statement-president-claudine-gay-stay-remain-antisemitism-israel-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGay's%20light%20academic%20publishing%20record%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20clearly%20not%20a%20good%20leader.%20She%20hasn't%20stepped%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20said%20Gay's%20appointment%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20cynical%20attempt%20to%20elevate%20a%20woman%20of%20color%20to%20the%20job%20rather%20than%20employing%20the%20most%20qualified%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20message%20it%20gets%20across%20is%2C%20'We%20don't%20take%20you%20so%20seriously%20so%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20hold%20you%20to%20a%20lower%20standard%20than%20everyone%20else.'%20That%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20case%20at%20all.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20women%20of%20color%20who%20are%2