ousands%20without%20power.%20Rescue%20teams%20continue%20to%20search%20for%20those%20trapped%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222765%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20left%20is%20an%20aerial%20view%20of%20a%20Japanese%20city%20before%20a%20major%20earthquake.%20On%20the%20right%2C%20is%20an%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20same%20region%20after%20the%20earthquake%2C%20showing%20massive%20destruction%20to%20homes%20and%20roads.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65948afbab6f2ebb11f85302%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22963%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20and%20after%20space%20photos%20of%20burned%20and%20destroyed%20buildings%20in%20Wajima.%3Cp%3ESatellite%20image%20%C2%A92024%20Maxar%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20town%20of%20Suzu%2C%20near%20the%20quake's%20epicenter%2C%2090%25%20of%20houses%20might%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20town's%20mayor%2C%20Masuhiro%20Izumiya%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fjapan%2Fleast-six-dead-after-huge-earthquake-rocks-japan-new-years-day-2024-01-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20catastrophic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Capsized%20boats%20and%20damaged%20buildings%20in%20Suzu%20City%20after%20a%20powerful%20earthquake%20hit%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659490ebec62ab5daf8028db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%20A%20satellite%20image%20of%20Suzu%20City%20shows%20capsized%20boats%20and%20damaged%20buildings.%20%3Cp%3ESatellite%20image%20%C2%A92024%20Maxar%20Technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20so%20powerful%20that%20the%20ground%20shifted%2C%20rising%20by%20o