0%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaster%20of%20U-turns%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20of%20mind%E2%80%9D.%20His%20mind%20seems%20to%20take%20a%20U-turn%20once%20every%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20when%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20raised%20a%20storm%20when%20he%20attacked%20the%20RSS%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Frss-conspiring-pralhad-joshi-karnataka-cm-h-d-kumaraswamy-2330852-2023-02-06%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20RSS%20wants%20to%20make%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20who%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20Karnataka%20culture%2C%20as%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fremarks-on-brahmins-misconstrued-says-hdk-101675798479325.html%5C%22%3Ewent%20on%20to%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Joshi%20belonged%20to%20the%20Peshwa%20community%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20indulging%20in%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%20politics%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%5Bmassacring%5D%20those%20who%20contributed%20to%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20patriotism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumaraswamy%20appealed%20to%20all%20communities%20not%20to%20fall%20prey%20to%20the%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20that%20would%20divide%20the%20country.%20He%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fwe-are-trying-to-shake-the-deep-rooted-agenda-of-bjp%2Farticle36868290.ece%5C%22%3Eduring%20an%20earlier%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20country%20were%20in%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20grip%20and%20that%20he%20had%20deeply%20studied%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20workings.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20was%20reading%20the%20book%20%3Ci%3EThe%20RSS%3A%20And%20the%20Making%20of%20the%20Deep%20Nation%3C%2Fi%3E%20by%20Dinesh%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20had%20attacked%20him%20for%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98B-team%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%20his%20statements%20were%20meant%20only%20to%20divide%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20in%20the%20upcoming%20by-polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-a-potentially-historic-election%5C%22%3EKarnataka%3A%20A%20Potentially%20Historic%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%202023%20Karnataka%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20fielded%2022%20Muslim%20candidates.%20It%20also%20vowed%20to%20restore%20the%204%25%20reservation%20for%20Muslims%20that%20was%20revoked%20by%20the%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20government.%20But%20it%20now%20seems%20that%20Muslim%20voters%20saw%20through%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csecular%E2%80%9D%20facade%20and%20voted%20en%20masse%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%2022%20candidates%20were%20defeated%20and%20many%20even%20lost%20their%20deposit.%20The%20JD(S)%20was%20wiped%20out%20in%20the%20elections.%20This%20is%20despite%20it%20having%20enjoyed%20support%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20the%20Old%20Mysore%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fkarnataka-election-results-jds-decimated-in-its-vokkaliga-stronghold%2Farticleshow%2F100220168.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewon%2041%20of%20the%2061%20seats%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20across%20seven%20districts%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20region.%20Its%20victories%20came%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20and%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20emerged%20as%20the%20new%20Vokkaliga%20strongman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20JD(S)%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own%20in%20the%20Vokkaliga%20belt%20in%20this%20election.%20Of%20the%20just%20over%20one%20crore%20votes%20polled%20in%2061%20seats%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20BJP%20polled%2024%2C60%2C429%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20just%20six%20lakh%20less%20than%20the%20JD(S)%E2%80%99s%2030%2C35%2C584%20votes%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fbjp-closes-gap-to-jds-in-old-mysuru-region%2Farticleshow%2F100237635.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20dismal%20performance%20not%20only%20put%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20but%20on%20the%20very%20existence%20of%20the%20JD(S).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQuestion%20of%20survival%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fi-stood-by-muslims-but-they-didnt-support-jds-says-kumaraswamy-2698811%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblamed%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20on%20Muslims%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhd-kumaraswamys-party-joins-bjp-led-nda-alliance-4414032%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eallied%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%202024%20election%20within%20four%20months.%20He%20also%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20another%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcongress-govt-may-fall-in-karnataka-claims-jds-leader-hd-kumaraswamy-11702224291013.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COperation%20Lotus%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Ftwo-jds-muslim-leaders-resign-following-alliance-with-bjp-in-karnataka%2Farticle67338938.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20Muslim%20leaders%20quit%20the%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20its%20decision%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Syed%20Shafiullah%2C%20state%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20said%20the%20party%20stood%20on%20principles%20of%20secularism%20while%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%9Cpreaches%2C%20propagates%20and%20acts%20on%20%5Ba%5D%20communal%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Bengaluru%3A%20On%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20party%2C%20JDS%20Karnataka%20Vice%20President%20Syed%20Shafiulla%20Saheb%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20with%20the%20party%20for%20the%20past%2030%20years.%20Our%20party%20stand%20on%20secular%20credentials%2C%20and%20we%20have%20always%20propagated%20the%20principles%20of%20Secularism%20to%20the%20voters%2C%20and%20to%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FS2okhgTmA0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FS2okhgTmA0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1705808247620518211%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20typical%20pettiness%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20questioned%20the%20contributions%20of%20Muslim%20leaders%20to%20his%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20father%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20former%20chief%2C%20believes%20that%20by%20rallying%20its%20original%20support%20base%20behind%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20can%20rejuvenate%20its%20electoral%20gains%3B%20but%20it%20might%20end%20up%20bolstering%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20own%20bastion.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20JD(S)%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20the%20BJP%20might%20in%202024%20achieve%20its%20distant%20dream%20of%20gaining%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20Mysore%20belt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20changing%20stance%20is%20known%20in%20political%20circles%20and%20he%20is%20euphemistically%20called%20%E2%80%9Ckingmaker%E2%80%9D%20during%20every%20election%20in%20Karnataka.%20During%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20will%20be%20the%20kingmaker%20after%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20fractured%20mandate%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fkarnataka%2F2023%2Fapr%2F20%2Fnot-a-kingmaker-but-will-be-king-says-hdk-2567561.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20replied%20pompously%20that%20he%20will%20be%20the%20king%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESecular%20kingmaker%20to%20(saffron)%20pawn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20Kumaraswamy%20is%20a%20sudden%20neo-convert%20and%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20Hindutva%20plank.%20The%20Kumaraswamy-led%20JD(S)%20has%20hobnobbed%20with%20the%20BJP%20earlier%20too%2C%20having%20formed%20the%20government%20twice%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201999%20as%20a%20breakaway%20faction%20from%20the%20Janata%20Dal.%20Gathering%20its%20strength%20from%20the%20Vokkaliga%20belt%20in%20southern%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20has%20been%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20kingmaker%20since%202004.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202004%20election%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20backed%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20post-poll%20alliance%2C%20following%20which%20Dharam%20Singh%20became%20chief%20minister%20of%20Karnataka.%20Within%2021%20months%2C%20though%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20pulled%20out%20its%20support%20and%20the%20Dharam%20Singh%20government%20collapsed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20shifted%20his%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20became%20chief%20minister%20of%20Karnataka%20with%20the%20help%20of%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20in%20a%20power%20sharing%20agreement%2C%20according%20to%20which%20Kumaraswamy%20would%20be%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20first%2020%20months%20followed%20by%20Yediyurappa%20for%20the%20remaining%2020%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-democracy-modi-shah%5C%22%3ETen%20Factors%20to%20Remember%20Amidst%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Win%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Defeat%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYediyurappa%20became%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20as%20well%20as%20finance%20minister%20in%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20after%2020%20months%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20refused%20to%20relinquish%20his%20post.%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20the%20JD(S)%20also%20supported%20his%20decision.%20He%20did%20resign%20some%20days%20later%20and%20Yediyurappa%20was%20made%20chief%20minister%20on%20November%2012%2C%202007.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Kumaraswamy%20again%20withdrew%20his%20support%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20collapse%20within%20a%20week%20of%20its%20formation.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20BJP%20came%20close%20to%20forming%20a%20government%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarly%20elections%20were%20called%20in%202008%20and%20Yediyurappa%2C%20riding%20the%20sympathy%20wave%20of%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post%20being%20snatched%20away%20from%20him%2C%20made%20a%20big%20comeback%20and%20emerged%20as%20chief%20minister%20and%20a%20powerful%20Lingayat%20leader.%20It%20was%20a%20historical%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20under%20Yediyurappa%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20the%20party%20made%20its%20entry%20in%20South%20India%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20similar%20situation%20occurred%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20no%20party%20won%20a%20majority.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20JD(S)%20formed%20a%20post-poll%20alliance%20and%20earned%20a%20majority%2C%20following%20which%20Kumaraswamy%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20After%20one%20year%2C%20his%20government%20lost%20its%20majority%20when%2013%20MLAs%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20three%20MLAs%20of%20the%20JD(S)%20resigned%20in%20%E2%80%9COperation%20Lotus%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20then%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20Yediyurappa%20at%20its%20helm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20demise%20of%20the%20Janata%20Party%3A%20From%20alternative%20politics%20to%20question%20of%20existence%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202006%2C%20when%20Kumaraswamy%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20famous%20Kannada%20writer%20Dr%20U.R.%20Ananthamurthy%20had%20questioned%20the%20JD(S)%E2%80%99s%20secular%20credentials.%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20famously%20asked%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2FU.R.-Ananthamurthy-controversies-in-political-cultural-arena%2Farticle60343404.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%20Dr%20Ananthamurthy%20was%20and%20what%20secularism%20meant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20dilly-dallying%20on%20secularism%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20Kumaraswamy.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20characteristic%20of%20parties%20associated%20with%20the%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20Janata%20Party%20was%20formed%20in%201977%20to%20oppose%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20(which%20later%20formed%20the%20BJP)%20as%20one%20of%20its%20significant%20constituent%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%20in%20seven%20states%2C%20namely%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20But%20over%20the%20years%2C%20opportunism%2C%20a%20weak%20secular%20rhetoric%2C%20family-centred%20politics%20and%20over-reliance%20on%20specific%20caste%20groups%20have%20led%20to%20the%20slow%20demise%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20%E2%80%9Calternative%20politics%E2%80%9D%20symbolised%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-rahul-gandhi-1977-2004-election%5C%22%3EThose%20Who%20Write%20Off%20the%20Opposition%20Must%20Not%20Forget%20the%20Electoral%20Surprises%20of%201977%20and%202004%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20constituent%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20later%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20coalition%20governments%20over%20the%20years%20and%20apparently%20had%20no%20problem%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20communal%20rhetoric%2C%20with%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20being%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20such%20a%20politics.%20He%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20weatherman%20of%20Indian%20politics%20due%20to%20his%20flip-flops%20from%20one%20alliance%20to%20another%20to%20be%20in%20power%20or%20a%20ministership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%20of%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20who%20had%20a%20strong%20base%20among%20Muslims%20in%20Bihar%20and%20had%20kept%20the%20state%20from%20the%20BJPs%E2%80%99%20clutches%2C%20has%20also%20succumbed%20to%20pressures%20from%20the%20BJP-driven%20ED%20and%20CBI%20raids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20another%20reminder%20that%20such%20a%20polity%20might%20keep%20one%20in%20power%2C%20but%20with%20no%20teeth.%20Such%20alliances%20only%20weaken%20the%20regional%20party%E2%80%99s%20strength%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20ambitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20managed%20to%20snuff%20out%20many%20regional%20parties%2C%20either%20with%20ED%20raids%20or%20impotent%20alliances.%20Ineffective%20regional%20or%20third%20parties%20will%20help%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20idea%20of%20a%20two-party%20system%20that%20eventually%20benefits%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Janata%20Parivar%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20to%20oppose%20the%20authoritarianism%20of%20the%20Emergency%20era%2C%20are%20now%20happy%20bedfellows%20with%20the%20fascist%20forces%20in%20power.%20From%20playing%20a%20supportive%20role%20to%20fighting%20for%20survival%2C%20the%20kingmaker%20has%20met%20its%20fate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESwati%20Krishna%20is%20an%20activist%20and%20political%20observer%20based%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704213720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F02200036%2FHDK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchanging-colours-of-h-d-kumaraswamy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kumaraswamy's%20mind%20seems%20to%20take%20a%20U-turn%20once%20every%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20when%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%20His%20changing%20stance%20is%20known%20in%20political%20circles%20and%20he%20is%20euphemistically%20called%20%E2%80%9Ckingmaker%E2%80%9D%20during%20every%20election%20in%20Karnataka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchanging-colours-of-h-d-kumaraswamy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20blames%20Israel%20for%20'cowardly%20assassination'%20of%20deputy%20leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704211380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-lebanon-dahiyeh-beirut_6410535.jpg%3F20240102201908%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhamas-deputy-head-saleh-arouri-killed-in-an-explosion-south-of-beirut-according-to-hezbollah-tv-13041022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20has%20said%20one%20of%20its%20top%20officials%2C%20Saleh%20al%20Arouri%2C%20has%20been%20killed%20in%20an%20explosion%20in%20Beirut%20-%20blaming%20the%20%26quot%3Bcowardly%20assassination%26quot%3B%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A480%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhamas-deputy-head-saleh-arouri-killed-in-an-explosion-south-of-beirut-according-to-hezbollah-tv-13041022%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhamas-deputy-head-saleh-arouri-killed-in-an-explosion-south-of-beirut-according-to-hezbollah-tv-13041022%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhamas-deputy-head-saleh-arouri-killed-in-an-explosion-south-of-beirut-according-to-hezbollah-tv-13041022%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MGNREGA%3A%20After%20Pushback%20on%20Aadhaar-Based%20Pay%2C%20Govt%20Defensive%2C%20Says%20May%20Consider%20Exemptions%20Case-by-Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09120730%2FAadhaar-cards.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Facing%20backlash%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20may%20consider%20exemptions%20from%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20(ABPS)%20for%20the%20payment%20of%20wages%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccase%20to%20case%E2%80%9D%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20for%20the%20Act%2C%20which%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households%2C%20was%20made%20mandatory%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023%20and%20kickstarted%20on%20Monday%20(January%201)%20after%20five%20extensions%20for%20state%20governments%20to%20calibrate%20their%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20requires%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20bank%20account%20and%20job%20card%20to%20be%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar.%20The%20account%20must%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98mapper%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnew-year-new-rule-for-mgnrega-workers%2Farticle67692863.ece%5C%22%3Edata%20provided%20by%20LibTech%20India%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20consortium%20of%20academics%20and%20activists%2C%207.6%20crore%20job%20cards%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20over%20the%20last%2021%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1992238%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20late%20on%20Monday%20(January%201)%20night%2C%20the%20Union%20rural%20development%20ministry%20said%20that%20exemption%20from%20the%20ABPS%20can%20be%20considered%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccase%20to%20case%20basis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20if%20any%20gram%20panchayat%20of%20a%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20having%20either%20technical%20%5Bproblems%5D%20or%20Aadhaar-related%20%5Bproblems%5D%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20may%20consider%20exemption%20from%20APBS%20on%20%5Ba%5D%20case%20to%20case%20basis%20till%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20condemned%20the%20ABPS%20for%20the%20MGNREGA%20and%20called%20it%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccruel%20new%20year%20gift%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20poor%20and%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20urged%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20weaponising%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%2C%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delayed%20wage%20payments%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20rolls%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20ministry%20in%20its%20statement%20said%20that%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnoticed%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20section%20of%20the%20newspapers%20has%20quoted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment%20should%20stop%20weaponizing%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delay%20wage%20payment%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20roll%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20MGNREGA%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdemand-driven%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20has%20brought%20%E2%80%9Ca%20transformation%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMahatma%20Gandhi%20NREGA%20is%20a%20demand%20driven%20scheme%20and%20is%20affected%20by%20various%20economic%20factors.%20Total%20number%20of%20registered%20job%20cards%20is%2014.32%20crore%2C%20out%20of%20which%20just%209.77%20crore%20(68.22%25)%20is%20active%20job%20cards.%20There%20is%20a%20total%20of%2025.25%20crore%20workers%2C%20out%20of%20which%20just%2014.32%20crore%20(56.83%25)%20are%20active%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20use%20of%20different%20technologies%20ranging%20from%20space%20technology%2Fremote%20sensing%20to%20IT%20enabled%20technology%2C%20has%20brought%20a%20transformation%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20refuted%20claims%20of%20any%20data%20being%20deleted%20due%20to%20the%20ABPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJob%20card%20of%20household%20can%20be%20deleted%20only%20in%20certain%20specific%20conditions%2C%20but%20not%20due%20to%20ABPS.%20Updation%2Fdeletion%20of%20job%20cards%20is%20a%20regular%20exercise%20conducted%20by%20the%20States%2FUTs.%20A%20job%20card%20can%20be%20deleted%20in%20case%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fake%20job%20card%20(incorrect%20job%20card)%2F%20duplicate%20job%20card%2F%20household%20not%20willing%20to%20work%2F%20family%20shifted%20from%20gram%20panchayat%20permanently%2F%20single%20person%20in%20job%20card%20and%20that%20person%20is%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20April%202022%20to%20till%20date%2C%20about%202.85%20crore%20job%20cards%20have%20been%20deleted%20by%20following%20the%20due%20process%20by%20the%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20specific%20pilot%20study%20as%20well%20as%20consultation%20was%20done%20before%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20National%20Mobile%20Monitoring%20System%20(NMMS)%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20claim%20in%20the%20statement%20that%2034.8%25%20of%20total%20registered%20workers%20and%2012.7%25%20of%20active%20workers%20are%20still%20ineligible%20for%20ABPS%20has%20no%20relevance.%20Because%20APBS%20is%20applicable%20only%20in%20case%20a%20registered%20beneficiary%20turns%20ups%20for%20wage%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20wage%20payment%20of%20unskilled%20workers%20through%20APBS%20to%20ensure%20the%20payment%20of%20beneficiaries%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20even%20in%20case%20of%20frequent%20change%20of%20bank%20account%20by%20the%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20if%20any%20gram%20panchayat%20of%20a%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20having%20either%20technical%20problem%20or%20Aadhaar-related%20problem%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20may%20consider%20exemption%20from%20APBS%20on%20case-to-case%20basis%20till%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704209505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09120730%2FAadhaar-cards.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Funion-government-may-consider-case-by-case-exemptions-to-abps-mgnregs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Monday%2C%20the%20Congress%20condemned%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20payment%20system%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98cruel%20new%20year%E2%80%99s%20gift%E2%80%99%20and%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%98weaponising%20technology%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Funion-government-may-consider-case-by-case-exemptions-to-abps-mgnregs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eurovision%20teases%20Caribbean%20announcement%20for%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704208080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-caribbean-guadeloupe_6410269.jpg%3F20240102151926%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feurovision-teases-caribbean-announcement-for-this-years-contest-13040987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eurovision%20organisers%20have%20teased%20an%20apparent%20Caribbean%20appearance%20at%20this%20year's%20contest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A128%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feurovision-teases-caribbean-announcement-for-this-years-contest-13040987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurovision-teases-caribbean-announcement-for-this-years-contest-13040987%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurovision-teases-caribbean-announcement-for-this-years-contest-13040987%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Directs%20Bihar%20Government%20to%20Make%20Public%20Break-Up%20of%20Caste%20Survey%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Bihar%20government%20to%20make%20the%20break-up%20of%20its%20caste%20survey%20data%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20enable%20those%20aggrieved%20to%20challenge%20the%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20however%2C%20declined%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20interim%20relief%3B%20the%20petitioners%20had%20challenged%20the%20survey%20and%20Patna%20high%20court%20order%20that%20upheld%20the%20Bihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20interim%20relief%20as%20they%20(the%20government)%20have%20a%20high%20court%20order%20in%20their%20favour.%20Now%20that%20the%20data%20has%20been%20put%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20are%20two%20to%20three%20aspects%20which%20remain.%20First%20is%20the%20legal%20issue%20%E2%80%93%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20high%20court%20judgement%20and%20legality%20of%20such%20an%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bench%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbihar-caste-survey-break-up-public-domain-inferences-challenged-sc-9092151%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Raju%20Ramachandran%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20the%20authorities%20had%20already%20begun%20implementing%20survey%20findings%20since%20the%20data%20was%20already%20out.%20He%20said%20the%20state%20government%20had%20already%20raised%20the%20reservation%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20and%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20(EWS)%20to%20a%20total%20of%2075%25%20from%20the%20existing%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20matter%20about%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20reservation%20should%20be%20challenged%20before%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%2C%20and%20said%20the%20entire%20matter%20needs%20to%20be%20heard%20at%20length.%20The%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioners%20in%20response%20said%20that%20they%20had%20already%20moved%20the%20high%20court%2C%20challenging%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20it%20as%20an%20important%20issue%2C%20Ramachandran%20said%20since%20the%20state%20government%20is%20already%20acting%20upon%20the%20data%2C%20the%20matter%20be%20listed%20next%20week%20so%20that%20the%20petitioners%20can%20argue%20for%20interim%20relief.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20interim%20relief%3F%20They%20(the%20Bihar%20government)%20have%20a%20high%20court%20judgement%20in%20their%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bench%20said%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20Shyam%20Divan%2C%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20the%20data%2C%20including%20the%20break-up%2C%20has%20been%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20anyone%20can%20see%20it%20on%20the%20designated%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20for%20the%20Bench%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20am%20more%20worried%20about%20is%20the%20availability%20of%20break-up%20of%20data.%20To%20what%20extent%20the%20government%20can%20withhold%20the%20data%3F%20You%20see%2C%20the%20entire%20break-up%20of%20data%20should%20be%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20so%20that%20anyone%20can%20challenge%20the%20inference%20drawn%20from%20it.%20Unless%20it%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20challenge%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20of%20irregularities%20in%20conducting%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20calling%20the%20data%20collected%20%E2%80%9Cfake%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20then%20told%20Divan%20to%20file%20a%20report%20on%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20February%205.%20The%20caste%20survey%20revealed%20that%20the%20OBCs%20and%20EBCs%20constituted%20a%20whopping%2063%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704205839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsc-directs-bihar-government-to-make-public-break-up-of-caste-survey-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%20unless%20such%20data%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20those%20aggrieved%20by%20it%20cannot%20challenge%20its%20findings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsc-directs-bihar-government-to-make-public-break-up-of-caste-survey-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20minus%2040C%20in%20Sweden%20and%20Finland%20as%20Nordic%20cold%20snap%20brings%20winter's%20coldest%20temperatures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704205800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-icy-sea-helsinki-finland_6410124.jpg%3F20240102125202%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsweden-and-finland-are-freezing-in-minus-40c-as-the-nordic-cold-snap-brings-winters-coldest-temperatures-13040925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finland%20and%20Sweden%20have%20recorded%20the%20coldest%20tem