n%20around%2020%20to%2030%20individuals%20in%20police%20uniforms%20entered%20a%20Pangal%20house%20in%20the%20Lilong%20Chingjao%20area%20of%20Thoubal%20district%2C%20looting%20cash%20and%20gold%20worth%20Rs%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20tried%20to%20intervene%2C%20following%20which%20the%20individuals%20in%20police%20uniforms%20fired%20at%20the%20Pangal%20residents%2C%20leading%20to%20four%20deaths%20and%20over%2014%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20are%20currently%20being%20treated%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Meitei%20Pangals%20met%20in%20Manipur%20and%20passed%20a%20resolution%20urging%20the%20government%20to%20arrest%20all%20culprits%20within%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20requested%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-terrorism%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20Pangal%20group%20has%20formed%20a%20joint%20action%20committee%20to%20the%20assist%20victims%20of%20the%20January%201%20incident%2C%20with%20Maulana%20Habibullah%20Sheikh%20appointed%20as%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20tragedy%20reported%20involving%20the%20Pangal%20community.%20In%20October%2C%20Sangomsumpham%20Sahir%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Sana%2C%20was%20allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-joint-action-committee-demands-cbi-probe-on-pangal-driver-death-case-699324-2023-10-23%5C%22%3Elynched%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20accusations%20of%20transporting%20goods%20for%20the%20Kuki%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahir%E2%80%99s%20family%20still%20awaits%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%2C%20Kukis%20cannot%20enter%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20Valley%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20likewise%20cannot%20enter%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kuki-dominated%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Meitei%20Pangals%20have%20historically%20acted%20as%20a%20link%20connecting%20both%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20Pangals%20are%20hesitant%20to%20speak%20on%20record%20about%20the%20violence%20affecting%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20police%20issued%20a%20press%20note%20on%20Monday%20discussing%20search%20operations%20in%20the%20Thoubal%20areal%20but%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20death%20of%20the%20four%20Pangals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20curfew%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20Thoubal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulana%20Mahmood%20Asa%E2%80%99d%20Madani%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Jamat%20Ulama-i-Hind%2C%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20urging%20decisive%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20this%20heinous%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaulana%20Madani%20stressed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20paramount%20responsibility%20to%20safeguard%20the%20lives%20and%20property%20of%20all%20citizens%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20high-level%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20the%20incident%E2%80%99s%20background%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20attempted%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Maulana%20Madani%20also%20appealed%20for%20reasonable%20compensation%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20comprehensive%20medical%20assistance%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20instructed%20state%20Jamiat%20leaders%20to%20actively%20participate%20in%20efforts%20to%20establish%20peace%20in%20the%20affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20this%20incident%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20communities%20other%20than%20Meiteis%20or%20Kukis%20were%20targeted%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20archbishop%2C%20Dominic%20Lumon%2C%20claimed%20that%20249%20churches%20belonging%20to%20Meitei%20Christians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-archbishop-claims-249-churches-burnt-in-36-hours-says-collapse-of-constitutional-machinery-11687135842800.html%5C%22%3Ewere%20destroyed%20within%2036%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20conflict%20breaking%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20both%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20situation%20in%20Moreh%2C%20a%20town%20at%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20has%20been%20deteriorating%20since%20December%2030%2C%20with%20firing%20ongoing%20in%20the%20surrounding%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704203937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmeitei-pangals-urge-arrest-of-new-years-day%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20group%20of%20Meitei%20Muslims%20(also%20known%20as%20Meitei%20Pangals)%20formed%20a%20joint%20action%20committee%20to%20assist%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20January%201%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20four%20members%20of%20the%20community%20were%20allegedly%20killed%20and%2014%20others%20were%20injured.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmeitei-pangals-urge-arrest-of-new-years-day%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oil%20prices%20volatile%20after%20latest%20attack%20on%20shipping%20container%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704203820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-maersk-container-ship_6410241.jpg%3F20240102145015%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2